<h1 class="center-align">Find Help!</h1>
<p>
  Technology often is a deciding factor between a good organization and a great organization.
  If you're like most organizations, you don't have the time OR desire to find qualified help for your technology needs.
</p>
<h4 class="center-align">That's where we come in.</h4>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12 m6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="card-title">Organizations</span>
        <p>
          If you are an church, charity, or other social organization looking for help with technology, we can match you up with
          individuals that desire to help, either for free or a small fee.
        </p>
        <%= link_to raw('Get Started<i class="material-icons right">send</i>'), new_help_request_path, :class => "btn waves-efect waves-light" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col s12 m6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="card-title">Individuals</span>
        <p>
          If you are an individual who wants to do good, we can help you find worthy organizations who are in need
          of technology. You could change the world, if you just found the right cause.
        </p>
        <%= link_to raw('Get Started<i class="material-icons right">send</i>'), new_help_offer_path, :class => "btn waves-efect waves-light" %>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
